{{Quote|His name is ''Arca''&hellip;he's quite ''alive''&hellip;but suffering mightily under the ''crushing power'' of the dark side.|King Ommin|<ref name="Tales of the Jedi – The Freedon Nadd Uprising 2">[[Tales of the Jedi – The Freedon Nadd Uprising 2|''Tales of the Jedi – The Freedon Nadd Uprising'' 2]]</ref>}}
'''Odojinya''' was a [[Sith/Legends|Sith]] incantation that created a '''[[Force net|dark side web]]''', a [[Sith sorcery/Legends|magic]] [[Force power/Legends|technique]] favored by [[Sith sorcerer]]s. When used successfully this power would summon strands of [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side]] energy that would wrap around the target and ensnare them in an unbreakable mesh. The lattice of dark energy would then effectively [[Sever Force/Legends|sever]] the being's connection to [[The Force/Legends|the Force]] and continuously sap their strength as well.

This technique was employed by [[King/Legends|King]] [[Ommin/Legends|Ommin]] of [[Onderon/Legends|Onderon]] to subdue [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Arca Jeth]].

